code: @Test public void cacheResolver() {     ConfigurableApplicationContext context = new GenericXmlApplicationContext("/org/springframework/cache/jcache/config/jCacheNamespaceDriven-resolver.xml").     DefaultJCacheOperationSource ci = context.getBean(DefaultJCacheOperationSource.class).     assertSame(context.getBean("cacheResolver"), ci.getCacheResolver()).     context.close(). }

@Test public void testCacheErrorHandler() {     JCacheInterceptor ci = ctx.getBean(JCacheInterceptor.class).     assertSame(ctx.getBean("errorHandler", CacheErrorHandler.class), ci.getErrorHandler()). }
